;255;255mcaută semantic: \"cât durează să pornească un model local mic?\"\u001b[39m                                                                 \r\u001b[2B\u001b[49m  \u001b[38;2;153;153;153mThought for \u001b[1m45s\u001b[22m, called plugin:total-recall:total-recall \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;2;255;255;255m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39m\u001b[1mRezultate \"cât durează să pornească un model local mic?\"\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B \u001b[4G \u001b[3G⚠️\u001b[5G \u001b[1mVector\u001b[13Gsearch încă down\u001b[22m — rezultatele de mai jos sunt\u001b[60Gtot\u001b[64GTF-IDF\u001b[71G(hybrid\u001b[79Ga\u001b[81Gcăzut\u001b[87Ggrațios\u001b[95Gpe\u001b[98Glexical).\u001b[108GConfirmă:\u001b[118Gtop-hit\u001b[126Ge\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BFlink\u001b[9G\"model\u001b[16Gfunctions\"\u001b[27G(coincidență\u001b[40Gpe\u001b[43G\"model\"),\u001b[53GNU\u001b[56Gmemoria\u001b[64Grelevantă.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B┌─────┬───────┬───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┬──────────┐\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B│\u001b[6G#\u001b[9G│\u001b[11GScore\u001b[17G│\u001b[57GTitle\u001b[101G│\u001b[104GVault\u001b[112G│\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B├\u001b[9G┼\u001b[17G┼\u001b[101G┼\u001b[112G┤\r\u001b[4C\u001b[1B1 \u001b[11G27.2 \u001b[19GApache\u001b[26GFlink\u001b[32G2.3\u001b[36G—\u001b[38GDataStream\u001b[49GJDBC\u001b[54G+\u001b[56GSQL model\u001b[66Gfunctions\u001b[76G(OpenAI/Triton)\u001b[103Gorg   \r\u001b[4C\u001b[2B2\u001b[11G9.7 \u001b[19GCer\u001b[23Getare GPU NVIDIA pen\u001b[45Gu Dell Latitude 5521\u001b[66G(Ollama) — decizie eGPU +\u001b[92GRTX\u001b[96G3060\u001b[103Gpersonal\r\u001b[4C\u001b[2B3\u001b[11G8\u001b[13G9\u001b[19GModel Inference (Flink SQL)\u001b[47G    \u001b[52G        \u001b[61G    \u001b[66G        \u001b[75G \u001b[77G       \u001b[85G    \u001b[90G \u001b[92G   \u001b[96G    \r\u001b[4C\u001b[2B4\u001b[11G\u001b[1m8.4\u001b[19GDemo laptop: gemma3:4b cold-load ≈ 2 min\u001b[22m\u001b[45;1H\u001b[42;3H\u001b[?