[233.68123, "o", "──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┴──────────┘\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mRăspunsul real la întrebare\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mMemoria #4\u001b[22m (\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mproject/demo-laptop-gemma3-4b-cold-load-2-min\u001b[39m)\u001b[62Ge\u001b[64Grăspunsul\u001b[74Gexact:\u001b[81Gpe\u001b[84Glaptopul\u001b[93Gde\u001b[96Gdemo, \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mgemma3:4b\u001b[112G\u001b[39m(model\u001b[119Glocal\u001b[125Gmic)\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bpornește din cold în \u001b[1m~2 min\u001b[22m, după care warm TTFT ≈ 1776ms.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[2B\u001b[1mDe ce n-a\u001b[13Gi\u001b[15Gșit #1\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[2BTF-IDF nu poate face puntea semantică \"pornească un model local mic\" →\u001b[74G\"cold-load ≈ 2 min\" —\u001b[96Gnu împărtășesc lexic. Adevărata\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcăutare semantică\u001b[21G(embeddings) ar\u001b[37Gfi ridicat #4 pe\u001b[54Gprimul loc.\u001b[66GAsta\u001b[71Ge\u001b[73Gexact\u001b[79Gsimptomul\u001b[89Gdescris\u001b[97Gîn\u001b[100Gmemoria\u001b[108G#6\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mtroubleshooting/total-recall-semantic-search-rebuild-native-deps-...\u001b[39m):\u001b[75Gvector\u001b[82Gsearch\u001b[89Gstă\u001b[93Gsilențios\u001b[103Goff.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mContext util găsit\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1m#2 + #8\u001b[22m — hardwar\u001b[23G-ul pe care \u001b[36Gulează modelul\u001b[51Glocal (Del\u001b[62G Latitude 5521, MX450 2GB,\u001b[91Gciz\u001b[95Ge\u001b[97GeGPU RTX 3060\u001b[111Gpentru\u001b[118GOllama).\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1m#9\u001b[22m — preferința echipei pentru \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mollama l\u001b[45Gunch claude\u001b[39m local.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[2BVrei să încerc rebuild-ul\u001b[29Gde\u001b[32Gnative\u001b[39Gdeps\u001b[44Gca\u001b[47Gsă\u001b[50Grepun\u001b[56Gvector\u001b[63Gsearch\u001b[70Gpe\u001b[73Gpicioare?\u001b[83G(memoria\u001b[92G#6\u001b[95Gare\u001b[99Gpașii\u001b[105Gexacti)\r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m✻\u001b[3G\u001b[38;2;218;124;92mActioning…\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m \u001b[38;2;153;153;153m(1m 11s · ↓\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;153;153;153m978 tokens)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m  ⎿  Tip: Use /btw to ask a quick side question without interrupting Claude's current work\u001b[39m\u001b[45;1H\u001b[42;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
